# ----------------------
# DO NOT ignore source code!
# These must be versioned:
# - Apex classes (*.cls)
# - Triggers (*.trigger)
# - Lightning components (*.cmp, *.app, *.evt, *.design, *.tokens)
# - LWC (force-app/main/default/lwc)
# - Visualforce pages (*.page)
# - Aura components (force-app/main/default/aura)
# - Static resources (*.resource)

# Therefore, DO NOT add lines like:
# *.cls
# *.trigger
# *.page
# etc.
